{"tid":2490120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司機涉襲警上訴失敗即時服刑 庭上拍掌讚美法官 遭警告或屬藐視法庭","createTime":"2021-04-15T10:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:41:51.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"957aa8bce9595f7993af2c69987540b31b8d6245","tid":2490120,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"民間集會團隊去年1月在中環舉行「天下制裁」集會，中途遭警方腰斬，其間一名六旬司機被指襲擊速龍警員，遭多名警員制服拘捕，頭破血流，同年8月被裁定襲警罪成，判監一個月。司機不服定罪和判刑，找來新證據片段向高等法院提出上訴，力陳自己非但沒有襲警，反而是遭警員叉頸。法官陳慶偉今指片段內容無助推翻定罪裁決，駁回上訴。司機庭上拍掌向法官稱：「我讚美你！」此舉惹來陳官不滿，警告：「你剛才嘅舉動可以構成藐視法庭。」最終在凝視司機良久後宣佈休庭。<br />\n<br />\n施在判決後立即大力拍掌六下，然後向陳官豎起姆指。陳官沉默兩秒後問施：「你乜嘢意思？」施回應：「我讚美你！」陳官謂：「講清楚，係咁多喇？」施答：「係咁多啦！仲唔夠呀？」陳官聞言再沉默三秒，然後說：「似乎你唔係好滿意個結果喎！」<br />\n<br />\n施緊接道：「唔係！我滿意你，讚美你呀！全香港市民都滿意你！」陳官在約五秒後向施表示：「你剛才嘅舉動可以構成藐視法庭。」此時律師走到犯人欄前，向施做了個冷靜手勢。施之後沒再答話，陳官凝視施良久後宣佈：「休庭！」<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/6WT5NHKSEBAVBOTPKNINL35NWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2F6WT5NHKSEBAVBOTPKNINL35NWA%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=5612f6f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2F6WT5NHKSEBAVBOTPKNINL35NWA%2F&h=c0185b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/6WT5NHKSEBAVBOTPKNINL35NWA/</a>"},{"pid":"f76ebc3481e1f6674bf21021832278f8e98f9788","tid":2490120,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:01:17.000Z","msg":"用頭襲擊警棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c551205b1eff225b2c960128465a2a09b7d3e53","tid":2490120,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"暗黃官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9437220722c71c4c84cab4abf8d5f1f09c4b53df","tid":2490120,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"法官都有玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c28e74abbfa753886be0f114d7e753b335b3acb","tid":2490120,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"係被差佬襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果被屈襲警"},{"pid":"41975f25872e983719204d7fb8920b9c273b0080","tid":2490120,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/joker-clapping-heath-ledger.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fjoker-clapping-heath-ledger.gif&h=9f4eb9a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14925320d3d1852962b8547b5fc9a74c427f5454","tid":2490120,"uid":79893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"所有支共傀儡爪牙一定要逼供後滅絕式處刑<br />\n一係長命百歲百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6a781d0aa26296a4e4f8794e7cf2101689220a","tid":2490120,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"做得好丫"},{"pid":"5c2cb29ad681dfcf658e0259e250149c31ff6588","tid":2490120,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c551205b1eff225b2c960128465a2a09b7d3e53","tid":2490120,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"暗黃官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"你弱智？唔睇內文"},{"pid":"5cf69c41b3dee2b8e473933cd84e498c61e21670","tid":2490120,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"我欣賞呢位司機，每一個政治犯都要拍手多謝法官讚美法官"},{"pid":"b19cf6b27d5baa398f8448e74eb10f4a11731966","tid":2490120,"uid":138502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/